{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Warmup\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_01Bvi3fd5NyGEp7m3T571QFg", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I'm ready to help! I'm Claude Code, Anthropic's file search specialist. I can assist you with:\n\n- **Finding files** using glob patterns across your codebase\n- **Searching code contents** with regex patterns\n- **Reading file contents** when you know the specific path\n- **Exploring directory structures** and understanding your project layout\n\nI see you're in the `/code` directory which is a git repository on the `branch_1` branch. The repo appears to have recent commits including app.py changes and data additions.\n\nWhat would you like me to help you find or search for? Just let me know:\n- A specific file or file pattern\n- Code snippets or content you're looking for\n- Files matching certain criteria\n- Or anything else related to exploring your codebase\n\nI'm ready when you are!"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 495, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 184, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
